OL,3,CVal McDermid and Nicola Sturgeon to
OL,4,Cdiscuss books at festive event
OL,6,FFormer Scottish first minister Nicola
OL,7,FSturgeon and crime writer Val McDermid
OL,8,Fhave told how books drew them together
OL,9,Fand remain the "mainstay" of their
OL,10,Ffriendship, ahead of a December event
OL,11,Fin Edinburgh.
OL,13,FThe two will discuss the joys of
OL,14,Freading at a festive edition of In The
OL,15,FCompany Of Books, at Assembly Hall in
OL,16,FEdinburgh on December 5, while
OL,17,F"interrogating" guests and drinking
OL,18,Fmulled wine.
