OL,3,CVal McDermid and Nicola Sturgeon to
OL,4,Cdiscuss books at festive event
OL,6,FThe women described their friendship
OL,7,Fas "improbable" and said that all
OL,8,Ftheir conversations revolve around
OL,9,Freading.
OL,11,FFormer journalist McDermid has sold
OL,12,Fmore than 19 million books
OL,13,Finternationally and her work has been
OL,14,Ftranslated into more than 40
OL,15,Flanguages. She has received six
OL,16,Fhonorary doctorates and is an Honorary
OL,17,FFellow of St Hilda's College, Oxford.
