OL,3,CVal McDermid and Nicola Sturgeon to
OL,4,Cdiscuss books at festive event
OL,6,FMSP Sturgeon was the longest-serving
OL,7,Fand first woman first minister of
OL,8,FScotland, and represents the Glasgow
OL,9,FSouthside constituency.
OL,11,FAfter the event in Edinburgh they will
OL,12,Fhost a similar one at the Glasgow
OL,13,FInternational Comedy Festival.
OL,15,FThey said: "Books are magic. Portable
OL,16,Fmagic, according to Stephen King. And
OL,17,Flike magic, books build bridges. In
OL,18,Four case, an improbable friendship
OL,19,Fbetween a passionate politician and
OL,20,FScotland's queen of crime.
