OL,3,CVal McDermid and Nicola Sturgeon to
OL,4,Cdiscuss books at festive event
OL,6,F"Our love of books is what first drew
OL,7,Fus together and it remains the
OL,8,Fmainstay of that friendship.
OL,10,F"Every conversation we have eventually
OL,11,Fmeanders round to the books we are
OL,12,Freading, what we've been enjoying,
OL,13,Fwhat has been making us laugh or cry,
OL,14,For keeping us on the edge of our
OL,15,Fseats. And now we want to share the
OL,16,Flove.
