OL,3,CVal McDermid and Nicola Sturgeon to
OL,4,Cdiscuss books at festive event
OL,6,F"First up, festive fun at Edinburgh's
OL,7,FAssembly Rooms with two stellar
OL,8,Fmystery guests, then off to the
OL,9,FGlasgow International Comedy Festival
OL,10,Fwhere we'll be joined by two top names
OL,11,Ffrom the comedy world.
OL,13,F"We'll be interrogating our guests
OL,14,Fabout the books that shaped them and
OL,15,Fwhy they love reading. Revelations
OL,16,Fgalore await as we explore the love
OL,17,Fand laughter between the covers."
OL,19,FThe event is part of Edinburgh's
OL,20,FChristmas.
