OL,7,Fproducers of Edinburgh's Christmas
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are thrilled to have Val and
OL,9,FNicola bring their in-conversation
OL,10,Fevent to Edinburgh's Christmas this
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,F"This is sure to be a highlight in the
OL,14,FChristmas calendar and we invite
OL,15,Feveryone to grab a glass of mulled
OL,16,Fwine and settle in for what will be a
OL,17,Fwitty, warm and insightful event."
